Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:40.95,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}在謎團重重的此世之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.95,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}將橫行的棋子落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.50,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}If I could burn it all down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:48.62,kanojo op cn,,0,0,0,,{\bord0}尋覓不見出口
